  ('civil-engineer-moex-00001', 'civil-engineer', 'civil-engineer-moex-114-1ca4f053', 'sub-civil-engineer-01', NULL, 'essay', '依照營造業法，目前之營造業共分為那三類？請比較各類之營業範圍、
